- 'Stars' in this context metaphorically represent 'players'; 
- 'constellations' refers to 'teams'; 
- 'shine' metaphorically stands for 'total hits', indicating the player's striking prowess; 
- 'radiant energy' represents 'total runs', symbolizing the player's overall contribution or energy on the field;
